<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197779>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14 – 24. Deuteraphorura pseudobosnaria: 14, dorsal chaetotaxy; 15, ventral chaetotaxy of the abdominal sterna; 16, ventral chaetotaxy of the head; 17, chaetotaxy of the antenna; 18, chaetotaxy of the labium (submentum); 19, labial palp with papillae A-E; 20, male genital plate; 21, antennal III sense organ, 22, postantennal organ; 23, chaetotaxy of the labrum; 24, distal part of leg III." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/197779/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197780>
    dc:description "FIGURES 25 – 31. Deuteraphorura pseudoinsubraria: 25, dorsal chaetotaxy; 26, ventral chaetotaxy of the abdominal sterna; 27, ventral chaetotaxy of the head; 28, chaetotaxy of the antenna; 29, antennal III sense organ; 30, postantennal organ; 31, distal part of leg III." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/197780/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197781>
    dc:description "FIGURES 32 – 38. Deuteraphorura apuanica: 32, dorsal chaetotaxy; 33, ventral chaetotaxy of the abdominal sterna; 34, ventral chaetotaxy of the head; 35, postantennal organ; 36, antennal III sense organ; 37, chaetotaxy of the antenna; 38, distal part of leg III." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/197781/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197782>
    dc:description "FIGURES 39 – 46. Deuteraphorura pseudoghidinii: 39, dorsal chaetotaxy; 40, ventral chaetotaxy of the abdominal sterna; 41, ventral chaetotaxy of the head and labium; 42, postantennal organ; 43, antennal III sense organ; 44, labial chaetotaxy of labial palp; 45, chaetotaxy of the antenna; 46, distal part of leg III." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/197782/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

